{"tid":2332154,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大個人第一次行獅子山","createTime":"2020-12-19T11:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T06:50:52.000Z","uid":213357,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"950a1bb444eef3bbce622ad009bd1e093856ff6c","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"最近一有時間就去行山，但加埋行過嘅山十隻手指數得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一年就嚟完，咁就想搵過特別啲嘅山行，最後就決定行獅子山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山對於香港人嚟講，都有一種情意結喺度。唔知係咪因為70年代香港電台嘅《獅子山下》嘅關係，獅子山從此變得不一樣，加上主題曲《獅子山下》，獅子山下精神或多或少因此而起。<br />\n<br />\n但到咗而家可能有人唔認同獅子山下精神，覺得獅子山下精神即係死做爛做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢個都要睇返唔同年代，可能會有唔同嘅意思。唔一定要認同嘅。但無疑獅子山係香港好有代表性嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n獅子山唔單止係創作嘅素材，甚至有人上山表達自己嘅訴求。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u34kYT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu34kYT1.jpg&h=c6c31a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce8xP0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8xP0H.jpg&h=40236331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（from wiki)<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家行山嗰時，覺唔覺得整路出嚟嘅人好厲害。無論係石屎路，古道，受薪與否都好，我都好敬佩呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁辛苦整條路出嚟畀人行。<br />\n<br />\n其實我哋嘅情況就好似咁，我哋只係整路嘅人。但我哋而家唔整，下一代就冇得行。整路嘅過程係好辛苦，但當你整完成條路，上到山之後就會發現，山上風景好靚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efTU3n8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefTU3n8.png&h=f99263d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識影相"},{"pid":"5811b92328eed35940a0cf8499eb0a948904b338","tid":2332154,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"大風到企唔穩 上到去要小心"},{"pid":"77450080c94fa570bc5b33df58b410fbe5620f63","tid":2332154,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"對條徑有無多D感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?或者多D相分享?<br />\n好似你咁少行山算唔算難行?<br />\n最尾張相iphone wide shot?"},{"pid":"f3e412a1b07427a4a300e9ea5339aa30dd72d4e3","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5811b92328eed35940a0cf8499eb0a948904b338","tid":2332154,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"大風到企唔穩 上到去要小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"真心驚驚地，獅頭嚿大石我都唔敢爬上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2987d0858667a8ed446112fbe10470d3ff5e24","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77450080c94fa570bc5b33df58b410fbe5620f63","tid":2332154,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"對條徑有無多D感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?或者多D相分享?<br />\n好似你咁少行山算唔算難行?<br />\n最尾張相iphone wide shot?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得都算難，上到差唔多頂之後，好多時都要手腳並用，但都還好。風景靚，天氣再好啲，清晰啲就更好。無錯是iPhone影的。唔係影得好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uCFY42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uCFY42.png&h=9f43f723&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqCe3wM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqCe3wM.png&h=e26ddb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xfHsYy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xfHsYy.png&h=b87625d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROJFeDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROJFeDD.png&h=89752a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影咗呢兩嚿石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2054b29259dd1a3d3eeac90a3a2acc2c8017a8","tid":2332154,"uid":250476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"尋晚先行完<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gs50ZG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGs50ZG3.jpg&h=cd93df7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4034f8841f2a5c1b7875f2cc36cba6c7ee13fcf","tid":2332154,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac2987d0858667a8ed446112fbe10470d3ff5e24","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77450080c94fa570bc5b33df58b410fbe5620f63","tid":2332154,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"對條徑有無多D感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?或者多D相分享?<br />\n好似你咁少行山算唔算難行?<br />\n最尾張相iphone wide shot?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得都算難，上到差唔多頂之後，好多時都要手腳並用，但都還好。風景靚，天氣再好啲，清晰啲就更好。無錯是iPhone影的。唔係影得好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uCFY42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uCFY42.png&h=9f43f723&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqCe3wM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqCe3wM.png&h=e26ddb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xfHsYy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xfHsYy.png&h=b87625d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROJFeDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROJFeDD.png&h=89752a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影咗呢兩嚿石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:05:51.000Z","msg":"獅子山算好撚易行，不過我畏高撚 去到山頂真心驚"},{"pid":"75a358630c0b6405c234ec3fbfd1c10da1d2f8b6","tid":2332154,"uid":293539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"950a1bb444eef3bbce622ad009bd1e093856ff6c","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"最近一有時間就去行山，但加埋行過嘅山十隻手指數得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一年就嚟完，咁就想搵過特別啲嘅山行，最後就決定行獅子山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山對於香港人嚟講，都有一種情意結喺度。唔知係咪因為70年代香港電台嘅《獅子山下》嘅關係，獅子山從此變得不一樣，加上主題曲《獅子山下》，獅子山下精神或多或少因此而起。<br />\n<br />\n但到咗而家可能有人唔認同獅子山下精神，覺得獅子山下精神即係死做爛做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢個都要睇返唔同年代，可能會有唔同嘅意思。唔一定要認同嘅。但無疑獅子山係香港好有代表性嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n獅子山唔單止係創作嘅素材，甚至有人上山表達自己嘅訴求。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u34kYT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu34kYT1.jpg&h=c6c31a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce8xP0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8xP0H.jpg&h=40236331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（from wiki)<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家行山嗰時，覺唔覺得整路出嚟嘅人好厲害。無論係石屎路，古道，受薪與否都好，我都好敬佩呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁辛苦整條路出嚟畀人行。<br />\n<br />\n其實我哋嘅情況就好似咁，我哋只係整路嘅人。但我哋而家唔整，下一代就冇得行。整路嘅過程係好辛苦，但當你整完成條路，上到山之後就會發現，山上風景好靚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efTU3n8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefTU3n8.png&h=f99263d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識影相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"你意思唔好破壞上一代鋪好嘅香港？"},{"pid":"6fd3c9381cd851381b2387253a9ae88238e3496f","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75a358630c0b6405c234ec3fbfd1c10da1d2f8b6","tid":2332154,"uid":293539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"950a1bb444eef3bbce622ad009bd1e093856ff6c","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"最近一有時間就去行山，但加埋行過嘅山十隻手指數得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一年就嚟完，咁就想搵過特別啲嘅山行，最後就決定行獅子山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山對於香港人嚟講，都有一種情意結喺度。唔知係咪因為70年代香港電台嘅《獅子山下》嘅關係，獅子山從此變得不一樣，加上主題曲《獅子山下》，獅子山下精神或多或少因此而起。<br />\n<br />\n但到咗而家可能有人唔認同獅子山下精神，覺得獅子山下精神即係死做爛做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢個都要睇返唔同年代，可能會有唔同嘅意思。唔一定要認同嘅。但無疑獅子山係香港好有代表性嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n獅子山唔單止係創作嘅素材，甚至有人上山表達自己嘅訴求。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u34kYT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu34kYT1.jpg&h=c6c31a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce8xP0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8xP0H.jpg&h=40236331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（from wiki)<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家行山嗰時，覺唔覺得整路出嚟嘅人好厲害。無論係石屎路，古道，受薪與否都好，我都好敬佩呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁辛苦整條路出嚟畀人行。<br />\n<br />\n其實我哋嘅情況就好似咁，我哋只係整路嘅人。但我哋而家唔整，下一代就冇得行。整路嘅過程係好辛苦，但當你整完成條路，上到山之後就會發現，山上風景好靚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efTU3n8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefTU3n8.png&h=f99263d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識影相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"你意思唔好破壞上一代鋪好嘅香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"邊句令你睇到咁嘅意思？"},{"pid":"fd8edff2e7566a85db8c460a3c75c938bc32f2f6","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4034f8841f2a5c1b7875f2cc36cba6c7ee13fcf","tid":2332154,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac2987d0858667a8ed446112fbe10470d3ff5e24","tid":2332154,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77450080c94fa570bc5b33df58b410fbe5620f63","tid":2332154,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"對條徑有無多D感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?或者多D相分享?<br />\n好似你咁少行山算唔算難行?<br />\n最尾張相iphone wide shot?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得都算難，上到差唔多頂之後，好多時都要手腳並用，但都還好。風景靚，天氣再好啲，清晰啲就更好。無錯是iPhone影的。唔係影得好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uCFY42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uCFY42.png&h=9f43f723&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqCe3wM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb